
                   toolbox/src/demos/OpenGL/insect README

              classic sgi insect demo moves into OpenGL space

    
    To Run:
           % insect
           LEFTMOUSE   - pan left or right depending upon "x-location"
                         of cursor (ie, left of window center, pan left)
           MIDDLEMOUSE - pan up or down depdning upon "y-location".
                       - both of the above move faster the further away
                         the mouse is from the window center.
           f/F         - toggle's movement of the eye
           ESC         - exit program

    Demonstrates:
           Lighting, Colormap (includin 8-bit machines),  display lists 
           (hierarchically-defined insect model) animation capabilities.

